  description="The essential starter words every new Scrabble player should memorise. QI, ZA, XI and 7 more high-scoring game-changers that win games from day one. Free."
  keywords="first words to learn scrabble, essential scrabble words, beginner scrabble vocabulary, QI scrabble, ZA scrabble, two letter words scrabble, high scoring short words, scrabble starter words"
>
